  "title": "Rudely",
  "sourceFile": "Waste_notes/rudely_N.htm",
  "encoding": "windows-1252",
  "html": "\n<div><center>\n<table>\n<tr>\n<td><font><img src=\"../images/R.gif\"/> <strong>So rudely\n        forced</strong></font><hr noshade=\"\"/>\n<p>Cf. Part III, l. 195. [Eliot's note] The reference in\n        this note and the previous also recall the following\n        lines from <i>The Hollow Men</i>: \"As wind in dry\n        grass/ Or rats' feet over broken glass/ In our dry\n        cellar\" </p>\n<p><font><em>reference topics</em></font></p>\n<table>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"Metamorphoses_IVPhil.htm\">Ovid's <em>Metamorphoses</em>,\n                </a><br/>\n<a href=\"Metamorphoses_IVPhil.htm\">book IV, Philomela</a></td>\n<td><a href=\"title_A.htm\"><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"Philomela.htm\">Philomela\n                and the Nightingale</a> </td>\n<td><a href=\"title_A.htm\"><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>The Hollow Men</td>\n<td><a href=\"title_A.htm\"><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"Waste_A.htm\"><font>back to \"The Waste Land\" </font></a></td>\n<td><a href=\"Burbank_A.htm\"><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</center></div>\n",
  "text": "So rudely forced Cf. Part III, l. 195. [Eliot's note] The reference in this note and the previous also recall the following lines from The Hollow Men : \"As wind in dry grass/ Or rats' feet over broken glass/ In our dry cellar\" reference topics Ovid's Metamorphoses , book IV, Philomela Philomela and the Nightingale The Hollow Men back to \"The Waste Land\"",
